    question: "Can the drone operate in rainy or windy conditions?",
    answer: "Yes, our aircraft are designed for field operations in challenging conditions. With an IP54 rating, they can operate in light rain and dusty environments. They can handle wind speeds up to 12 m/s (26 mph), making them suitable for most operational scenarios."
  },
