    question: "What kind of warranty and support do you offer?",
    answer: "We provide a standard 2-year manufacturer's warranty covering all hardware defects. Extended warranty options are available. Our support team offers 24/7 technical assistance, and we maintain a global network of certified repair centers."
  },
